description:
We'll have a variety of talks on mobile development and the ecosystem. We're still working on additional speakers which will be confirmed in due course. If you have a talk or want to share any updates with the group since the last meetup, i.e you've released a new app, or open-source project please let us know and we'll try to carve out some space for this.

CFP form[ http://cfp.swmobile.org](http://cfp.swmobile.org)

**Talks**

* Placeholder while we organiser speakers

**Timings:**
18:30 Doors open, Food, typically pizza with veg and vegan options available & drink
19:00 Intro and talks
19:45 Break
20:00 talks
20:45 Finish (tidy up)
21:00 Continue the conversation at near by pub (TBC)

If you are a first time member and/or don't know anyone and would rather pre-meet so you arrive with others please drop us an message via meetup.com (or @scottyab twitter) and we'll arrange it.

See you there!
title: April Tech Talk Night
